{"tid":2451652,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓《都市怪談2》爆「10偶像同台演出」　Oh My Girl成員Arin當女主角","createTime":"2021-03-18T09:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T11:38:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc55bb895c72a3451f95806a1750f6d959660ff9","tid":2451652,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"南韓娛樂產業興盛，戲劇、電影和音樂在全世界都有亮眼的成績和人氣，近日網劇《都市怪談》即將推出第二季，17日被爆出演員陣容，一整排名單就有10個偶像，掀起粉絲圈的討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5511/d5511300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5511%2Fd5511300.jpg&h=0d245fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《都市怪談》2020年開播，第二季是電影。（圖／翻攝自Netflix）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《JOYNEWS24》報導，演藝圈相關人士透露《都市怪談2》將找來Monsta X隊長Shownu、BTOB成員李旼赫、李浩沅、Lovelyz成員徐智秀、宇宙少女成員雪娥和EXY、阿歷薩、金度允（音譯，김도윤）、是Oh My Girl成員Arin和Golden Child成員奉宰鉉演出。其中Arin將擔任女主角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5511/5511347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5511%2F5511347.jpg&h=e22ca3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《都市怪談2》被爆找來多位偶像演出。（圖／翻攝自Shownu、李旼赫、徐智秀 IG、Oh My Girl臉書、Golden Child推特）<br />\n<br />\n除了這10位偶像，還有演員鄭元昌、李垂珉（李秀敏）和李烈音，電影製作商Zanybros（쟈니브로스）曾透露，《都市怪談2》（暫定）目標是在2021年上半年、最晚夏天上映。"},{"pid":"1d757864966803b469389de535f703e5d29efee1","tid":2451652,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:16:24.000Z","msg":"又唔知陪左邊個老細幾晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c59167737fb07d7e04d42ca0a29133bbd08bca0","tid":2451652,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"2 hit 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f